        "You will now proceed through a series of experimental blocks\n\nThere will be ten (10) blocks in total, each consisiting of eight (8) rounds of the box task.\nAfter each round you will respond to the workload survey and then you will continue the task.\n\nBetween blocks you you will be given updates on your progress including your coin total, and invited to take a short break before continuing."
      ]
