  "instructions": {
    "showTaskTitleCard": false,
    "showBlockLabel": false,
    "preBlockBeforeBlockIntro": true,
    "skipBeforeBlockScreensOnRepeat": true,
    "introPages": [
      {
        "html": "<div style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.45;'>Welcome to the box game! This guy is called Boxy:<p><img src='assets/evander-bricks/boxy.png' alt='Boxy' style='max-height: 120px; height: 100%; width: auto;'/></p><p>Boxy loves colllecting coins from the boxes in his factory. Your job is to help open as many boxes as you can within a time limit. Each trial will display four conveyor belts with moving boxes. Opening a box will give you a random reward in the form of coins.<p>Sometimes you will see a present - these are worth more coins. More coins makes Boxy happy!<p><img src='assets/evander-bricks/brick_types.png' alt='Present vs Crate example' style='max-width: 300px; width: 100%; height: auto;'/><p>The width of a box or present indicates the amount of work it takes to open. Each line ends at a furnace. If any box or present reaches the furnace, it is destroyed and you will lose coins instead of gaining them. Losing coins makes Boxy sad.</div>"
      },
      {"html": "<div style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.45;'>To open a box, you must click and hold the left mouse button while your cursor is within the highlighted window around it. You need to try to hold the mouse button for {bricks.completionParams.target_hold_ms} ms ({bricks.completionParams.target_hold_ms / 1000} s), then release it.<p><img src='assets/evander-bricks/boxy_with_box.png' alt='Boxy with box' style='max-height: 120px; height: 100%; width: auto;'/></p><p>The closer to exactly {bricks.completionParams.target_hold_ms} ms ({bricks.completionParams.target_hold_ms / 1000} s) you hold the button for, the more of the box will disappear.\n\nIf you hold the button for too long or short, less of the box will be removed. By working hard at estimating {bricks.completionParams.target_hold_ms} ms ({bricks.completionParams.target_hold_ms / 1000} s) holds, you can clear the boxes faster and ensure you don't lose coins from boxes being destroyed."},
      "We will start with a practice of the click-and-hold task."
    ],
