      { "html": "<div style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.45; style='text-align:center; margin-bottom:12px''>Great work, time for a short break.<p><img src='assets/evander-bricks/break_images/break{summaryIndex1}.png' style='max-width: 480px; width: 100%; height: auto; image-rendering:pixelated'><p>Your current coint balance is: {experimentPoints}.</p><p>Across the experiment you have opened {blockCleared} boxes, and let {blockDropped} boxes be destroyed.</div>" }],
      "metrics": {
